MAN [OVER RADIO]:
<i>This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.</i>

1150
01:34:07,225 --> 01:34:10,137
<i>KDK 1 calling KDK 12.</i>

1151
01:34:10,435 --> 01:34:12,221
<i>Are you receiving me?</i>

1152
01:34:15,399 --> 01:34:18,893
<i>This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.</i>

1153
