<i>KDK 1 calling KDK 12.</i>

1154
01:34:22,239 --> 01:34:23,900
<i>Do you read me?</i>

1155
01:34:28,246 --> 01:34:31,283
<i>This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.</i>

1156
